  "description": "<p>🎉 Events & Marketing Associate (Entry-Level)</p><p>Love meeting people? Enjoy high-energy environments? Not into boring desk jobs? 👀</p><p>Join our Events & Marketing Team and be part of exciting events, roadshows, and brand activations!</p><p><br /></p><p>💼 What You’ll Do</p><p>Run fun on-ground events & promotions</p><p>Represent brands and engage with public 🗣️</p><p>Work with a supportive team to hit goals 🎯</p><p><br /></p><p>🌟 What We’re Looking For</p><p>Positive attitude & strong work ethic</p><p>Willing to learn and step up</p><p>Comfortable talking to people</p><p><br /></p><p>🎁 What You’ll Get</p><p>Fun & energetic team vibes 🎉</p><p>Training & mentorship (no experience needed!)</p><p>Incentives & bonuses 💰</p><p>Clear growth opportunities 📈</p>",
